  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Excellent hot and cold buffet breakfast</li>
<li>A superb and flexible hotel 'Culinary Pass' can be pre-booked and redeemed to the value of Sfr100 per person daily in any of the hotel’s restaurants, bars and also includes room service (credit can be accumulated each day).</li>
<li>Free complimentary mini bar of soft drinks in all rooms</li>
<li>The gourmet a la carte Prato Broni has been awarded a Michelin star </li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>An elegant luxury hotel, offering a sublime setting and superb facilities in the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a>. Built in 1879, this historic hotel offers modern facilities, excellent dining, and warm service. The unique restaurants prepare cuisine ranging from the traditional to the modern and you can enjoy the freedom of all the restaurants during your stay with a dine-around package (extra). A choice of dining options include the Alpine Gourmet Prato Borni (One Michelin star), offers à la carte Valais region dining with a new and imaginative twist, and Brasserie Lusi which serves the very best of French brasserie cuisine and international dishes.</p>
<p>There is also the Swiss Cheese restaurant for a perfect fondue night. Enjoy a relaxing evening with gentle piano music in <em>The Stars Bar</em>. The spa and wellness area offers a relaxing setting for a dip in the warm pool. There is also a Finnish sauna, Turkish bath, whirlpool, large indoor pool and a range of massages available.</p>]]></description>
